50|$|The {{elements}} of account stated are: (1) prior transactions {{between the parties}} which establish a debtor-creditor relationship; (2)an express or implied agreement between the parties as to the amount due; and (3) an express or <b>implied</b> <b>promise</b> from the debtor to pay the amount due.|$|E
